                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>The Lexington Presbytery met in Staunton and dissolved the pastoral
                    relation between the Rev. William T. Richardson and the Waynesboro Church he
                    headed for 23 years. He leaves with the regrets of the congregation and his
                    colleagues but will soon take charge of the Warrenton Church. In the meantime,
                    the Rev. Robert C. Walker will handle church business.</summary>
                <note/>
